Task Name: 1.3: Simultaneous TA & MAM01 transfection with double selection
Parent Name: Aim 1: Cell Line Generation
Task Content:
Deliver MAM01 and transactivator simultaneously into CHOZN Elite WT parent line. Engineer EF1a GAVPO vector with blasticidin selection marker for cotransfection with antibody and double selection. All current opto chassis hosts do not have a selection marker for the transactivator, which can cause the transactivator to be lost over time. Introduction of EF1a GAVPO with a selection marker will increase transactivator stability.

Cell Line: CHOZN Elite WT

Constructs:
P_2117_CMV_MAM01_Hc_BGHpolyA_CMV_MAM01_Lc_BGHpolyA_CMV_MAM01_Lc_BGHpolyA_SV40p_Glutamine_Synthetase_BGHpolyA
